{
  "texts": [
    "After undergoing pre-training and instruction tuning, the LLMs have attained extensive world knowledge and proficient planning capabilities.",
    "Recent work [20,21,37,45] exploit these powerful capabilities to generate better control plans for robots and agents.",
    "ReAct [55] effectively integrates the action decision with planning and results in promising performance.",
    "SwiftSage [28] integrates fast and slow thinking to solve complex tasks.",
    "However, these methods lack the ability to learn from past experiences, which allows for better task planning."
  ]
}